column5: You are wrong! I hope you are like me and deep down you know you want to keep on fighting the depression and sadness, but can’t figure out how. It sucks that your best wasn’t good enough in the past, but that is the past. Please remember that you owe it to yourself to give your best a chance to pull of the upset victory over depression in the future. Don’t give up you got this.
On behalf of everyone else and myself thank you all for not giving up.
